The place was very clean and well appointed, lovely decor in our tiny standard room (the bathroom was huge and very nice).	The hotel itself is lovely and well-maintained with comfortable rooms; breakfast was the standard European variety and well done.	Staff are very friendly and helpful and the price we paid was pretty good for the standard and location of the hotel.	I have attached photos of the wheelchair accessible room and though not the standard we are used to in North America, it was pretty good after our experience in Barcelona.